---
description: Keep GoodWorkflows local and cluster templates, workflow lists, and image manifests aligned
globs: "{template/**,scripts/ci/**,scripts/image-manifest.txt,main.nf,.github/workflows/**}"
alwaysApply: false
---

# Template Parity

- Treat `main.nf` `supportedWorkflows` as the workflow-list source of truth.
- Treat `scripts/image-manifest.txt` as the container-image source of truth.
- Keep `template/gw/setup.sh`, `scripts/ci/cache_container_images.sh`, and image manifests aligned.
- Keep `template/gw/run.sh`, `template/gw/check_workflows.sh`, docs, schema, and CI workflow matrices aligned when workflows change.
- Preserve intentional local/cluster differences: profile, container runtime, LabKey credential handling, SBATCH metadata, and ANSI logging.
- For new workflows, add samplesheet generation or registry metadata when the default `samplesheet.csv` is not enough.
